'''Power rods''' were mysterious crystalline formations that grew in the cavern of [[Haven Base]] on [[Arbra/Legends|Arbra]]. They perpetuated huge amounts of energy and released harmless bolts of lightning. They were the main source of energy on which the [[Hoojib/Legends|Hoojibs]] fed. They also served as the power supply for the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] in Haven Base. Unfortunately, the heat they generated also attracted a [[slivilith]].

[[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] believed they were powered by [[The Force/Legends|the Force]]. When the [[self-perpetuating force screen]], the [[Grotto City]], and the [[Darker]] were destroyed, Luke was afraid the power rods had lost the source of their energy, and Rebel technicians were notified to monitor the rods' output for decrease.

